name: Sentimental Soft Sail
description:
"In a hot tropical solar degree,
We are sailing through the depth
of a gloomy bright day.
No shade is covering us from the angry sun above,
As the ancient boat tries to flow
with a Sharkshrimp The Allergy Maker."
.
